        "content": "## I.LG — Lead Gurus Daily Pull\nThin cron: daily ~06:00 ET (workflow timezone America/New_York) POST to LP-MCP `/n8n/leadgurus/daily-pull`, which does the whole pipeline: GET Lead Gurus summary (client/territory/channel) → upsert `ft_daily_summary` / `ft_summary_territory` / `ft_summary_channel`; GET leads (paginate `next`) → upsert `ft_leads`; (gated, default OFF) match GHL contact by email→phone and write `ft_*` customFields.\n\n**Logic lives in LP-MCP `src/leadgurus-ingest.js`.** API key `LEAD_GURUS_API_KEY` is on the LP-MCP Railway service. customFields ONLY — never tags.\n\n**Backfill (manual):** `POST https://lp-mcp-production.up.railway.app/n8n/leadgurus/backfill` with `{ \"start_date\": \"2026-01-01\" }` — walks monthly windows to seed history.",
